sources.description:
A drug-dealing pharmacist quits his criminal activities when he falls in love with a woman who wants nothing to do with drugs. But when a psychotic killer informs the pharmacist that they are now business partners, quitting is no longer an option.

2010.  Stars: Corey Loranger, Anna-Maria LeMaistre, Chris Craddock
